Instructions:

  1. set environment variable ANTICIPATOR with tool's path

  2. load "anticipator.il" in your .cdsinit file, e.g.:
  load(strcat(getShellEnvVar("ANTICIPATOR") "/src/anticipator.il"))

  3. start Virtuoso

  4. type "anticipator": the Anticipator menu should appear

  5. run Anticipator Setup on the libraries which need "hspice" views
  to be created

  6. run Anticipator
